::Zardus/Striker/DevilDuer::

Zardus slams into a tree, firing a shot at Sniper and slamming into another 
tree from Striker's shot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker grins. "We'll leave as so-" the maximal is interrupted by DevilDuer, 
who lands behind him, shooting him in the back.

"Well well..." Zardus says, looking at the two maximals, "I guess you'll be 
leaving without a pod...."
